title: $:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/context-templates/thread
tags: $:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/context-template
template-name: Discussion thread
template-description: Walks parent chain to reconstruct a conversation thread
output-mode: text
output-target: new-tiddler
output-title-template: $(currentTiddler)$/Reply Draft
output-tags: llm-generated draft
output-fields: {"parent": "$(currentTiddler)$", "author": "llm-draft"}
inject-as: user-message

Discussion thread (oldest first):

<$list filter="[all[current]tagging[]sort[created]]">
[<$transclude field="author" mode="inline"/>] <$transclude field="text" mode="inline"/>
</$list>

Latest message:
[<$transclude field="author" mode="inline"/>] <$transclude field="text" mode="inline"/>
